# HospitRL Environment

An OpenEnv compliant reinforcement learning environment for hospital ward management.

## Motivation
This environment simulates the real-world challenge of medical staff allocation across different hospital wards (ICU, ER, General) to manage patient pressure and staff fatigue.

## Observation Space
- Wards: List of ICU, ER, and General ward states (patients, staff, fatigue).
- Hospital Pressure: Global metric (0.0 to 1.0) indicating system strain.

## Action Space
- source_ward: Integer (0-2)
- target_ward: Integer (0-2)
- staff_count: Integer (Number of staff to move)

## Setup
1. pip install .
2. hospitrl-server
